      "title": "All-time record price for Halpewatte Uva Estate",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Halpewatte Uva Estate is located in Bandarawela, and comes under the purview of Halpewatte Estate Ltd. An all-time record price of Rs. 2,550 per kg for a BOPSP in the Uva Medium Category was achieved by the estate at the tea auction held on 19 July.",
        "This invoice of tea was purchased by LOLC Holdings PLC and was marketed and sold by John Keells PLC."
      ],
